README.md
     1‚Üí# python-dotenv
     3‚Üí[![Build Status][build_status_badge]][build_status_link]
     4‚Üí[![PyPI version][pypi_badge]][pypi_link]
     5‚Üí
     6‚Üípython-dotenv reads key-value pairs from a `.env` file and can set them as
     7‚Üíenvironment variables. It helps in the development of applications following the
     8‚Üí[12-factor](https://12factor.net/) principles.
     9‚Üí
    10‚Üí- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
    11‚Üí- [Other Use Cases](#other-use-cases)
